Package com.zanderwohl.chunks.World

Class Volume

java.lang.Object
com.zanderwohl.chunks.World.Volume
public class Volume
extends java.lang.Object
A unit of blocks in three dimensions that has a height, width and depth. Is stored as a single file, and is given a generator in order to generate and populate its own contents when called to do so.
